#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:38
msgid "Environment variables"
msgstr "Promenljive okruženja"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:40
msgid ""
"You can configure some aspects of QGIS Server by setting **environment "
"variables**."
msgstr ""
"Neke aspekte QGIS Server-a možete konfigurisati postavljanjem **promenljivih"
" okruženja**."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:43
msgid ""
"According to the HTTP server and how you run QGIS Server, there are several "
"ways to define these variables. This is fully described in "
":ref:`httpserver`."
msgstr ""
"U zavisnosti od HTTP servera i načina na koji pokrećete QGIS Server, postoji"
" nekoliko načina za definisanje ovih promenljivih. Ovo je u potpunosti "
"opisano u :ref:`httpserver`."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:53
