#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:65
msgid "QGIS_PLUGINPATH"
msgstr "QGIS_PLUGINPATH"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:65
msgid ""
"Useful if you are using Python plugins for the server, this sets the folder "
"that is searched for Python plugins."
msgstr ""
"Korisno ako koristite Python dodatke za server, ovo postavlja folder u kojem"
" se traže Python dodaci."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:76
msgid "QGIS_PROJECT_FILE"
msgstr "QGIS_PROJECT_FILE"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:71
msgid ""
"The ``.qgs`` or ``.qgz`` project file, normally passed as a parameter in the"
" query string (with *MAP*), you can also set it as an environment variable "
"(for example by using ``mod_rewrite`` Apache module)."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka projekta ``.qgs`` ili ``.qgz``, obično prosleđena kao parametar u "
"niski upita (sa *MAP*); možete je postaviti i kao promenljivu okruženja (na "
"primer korišćenjem Apache modula ``mod_rewrite``)."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:75
msgid ""
"You may also indicate a project stored in PostgreSQL, e.g. "
"``postgresql://localhost:5432?sslmode=disable&dbname=mydb&schema=myschema&project=myproject``"
" or inside a geopackage file, e.g. "
"``geopackage:/path/to/geopackage/file.gpkg?projectName=myProjectName``."
msgstr ""
"Takođe možete naznačiti projekat sačuvan u PostgreSQL-u, npr. "
"``postgresql://localhost:5432?sslmode=disable&dbname=mydb&schema=myschema&project=myproject``"
" ili unutar geopackage datoteke, npr. "
"``geopackage:/path/to/geopackage/file.gpkg?projectName=myProjectName``."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:81
msgid "QGIS_SERVER_ALLOWED_EXTRA_SQL_TOKENS"
msgstr "QGIS_SERVER_ALLOWED_EXTRA_SQL_TOKENS"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:82
msgid ""
"Comma separated list of strings that represent the allowed extra SQL tokens "
"accepted as components of a feature filter."
msgstr ""
"Lista niski razdvojenih zarezima koje predstavljaju dozvoljene dodatne SQL "
"tokene prihvaćene kao komponente filtera objekata."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:84
#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:125
#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:222
