msgstr "Izgradnja iz naziva servera i protokola servera."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:264
msgid ""
"In the last four cases, the resulting Service URL is based on the ``MAP`` "
"parameter provided in the query string and on the incoming path request."
msgstr ""
"U poslednja četiri slučaja, rezultujući URL servisa zasniva se na parametru "
"``MAP`` datom u niski upita i na dolaznom zahtevu putanje."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:273
msgid "QGIS_SERVER_SHOW_GROUP_SEPARATOR"
msgstr "QGIS_SERVER_SHOW_GROUP_SEPARATOR"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:270
msgid ""
"Defines whether a group separator (e.g. thousand separator) should be used "
"for numeric values (e.g. in GetFeatureInfo responses). The default value is "
"``0``."
msgstr ""
"Definiše da li za numeričke vrednosti treba koristiti separator grupa (npr. "
"separator hiljada) (npr. u GetFeatureInfo odgovorima). Podrazumevana "
"vrednost je ``0``."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:287
msgid "QGIS_SERVER_TRUST_LAYER_METADATA"
msgstr "QGIS_SERVER_TRUST_LAYER_METADATA"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:279
msgid ""
"This is an option at the project level to improve project read time by using"
" the vector layer extents defined in the project metadata and disabling the "
"check for PostgreSQL/PostGIS layer primary key uniqueness."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je opcija na nivou projekta za poboljšanje vremena čitanja projekta "
"korišćenjem obuhvata vektorskih slojeva definisanih u metapodacima projekta "
"i onemogućavanjem provere jedinstvenosti primarnog ključa PostgreSQL/PostGIS"
" sloja."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:283
msgid ""
"Trusting layer metadata can be forced by setting this variable to ``1`` or "
"``true``. The vector layer's extent will then be the one defined in the "
"project, and the PostgreSQL/PostGIS layer's primary key defined in the data "
"source is considered as unique without a check."
msgstr ""
"Poverenje metapodacima sloja može se prisiliti postavljanjem ove promenljive"
" na ``1`` ili ``true``. Obuhvat vektorskog sloja tada će biti onaj definisan"
" u projektu, a primarni ključ PostgreSQL/PostGIS sloja definisan u izvoru "
"podataka smatra se jedinstvenim bez provere."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:288
msgid "Do not use it if layers' extent is not fixed during the project's use."
msgstr ""
"Ne koristite je ako obuhvat slojeva nije fiksan tokom korišćenja projekta."

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:293
msgid "QGIS_SERVER_WCS_SERVICE_URL"
msgstr "QGIS_SERVER_WCS_SERVICE_URL"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:293
#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:299
#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:317
#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:323
msgid ""
"This is an option to set the service URL if it is not present in the "
"project. See :ref:`QGIS_SERVER_SERVICE_URL <qgis_server_service_url>` for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je opcija za postavljanje URL-a servisa ako nije prisutan u projektu. Za"
" više informacija pogledajte :ref:`QGIS_SERVER_SERVICE_URL "
"<qgis_server_service_url>`."

