#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:349
msgid "Settings summary"
msgstr "Rezime podešavanja"

#: ../../docs/server_manual/config.rst:351
msgid ""
"When QGIS Server is starting, you have a summary of all configurable "
"parameters thanks to environment variables. Moreover, the value currently "
"used and the origin is also displayed."
msgstr ""
"Kada se QGIS Server pokreće, imate rezime svih podesivih parametara "
"zahvaljujući promenljivama okruženja. Osim toga, prikazuje se i trenutno "
"korišćena vrednost i njeno poreklo."

